spirit:component.spirit:name: MainDesign_v_rgb2ycrcb_0_0
spirit:component.spirit:description: The Xilinx RGB to YCrCb Color Space Converter LogiCORE with built-in support for 5 formats and 3 range standards. The implementation is a simplified 3x3 constant coefficient matrix multiplier, which uses only 4 multipliers exploiting the inter-relations of RGB to YCrCb coefficients. The module is optimized to take advantage of multiply-add capabilities of DSP slices.
